<br>
Vel Diamond rings +8 all<br>
Vel BD Bracers +9 MFDP/+11C/+30MANA<br>
Electrum BD Earings +4M/+6FC/+11DP/+15MANA<br>
<br>
Just wearing a full set of these gives:<br>
+42M/+46F/+50C/+56D/+56P/+90MANA<br>
<br>
Also nice is the Sarnak Battle Shield, +10MFC, also +25AC, +5STR<br>
<br>
If you can get these 7 items together, that will get you pretty close in all 5 categories, then you can fill in the gaps with other items as you wish. <p>Tatanka WolfDancer, 56th Druid<BR>
Ethereal, 7th Hammer</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uduranstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>duranstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#333399>(1/10/02 12:38:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26194.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a few others</span><hr size=1> Crown of the froglock kings 20FC<br>
cloak of the ice bear 20C<br>
<br>
plat Blue diamond tiara 8 all<br>
<br>
gold diamond mask has bonus to all, but i forget what exactly.<br>
<br>
basicly what Tatankawd said: get a set of blue diamond, diamond gear and then fill in the cracks.  Fire and cold are easy, magic and poison are a bit harder.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umissfoxfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miss Foxfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 815<br> <font color=#333399>(1/10/02 1:53:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26194.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://gwynhyfar.homestead.com/files/smallface.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: a few others</span><hr size=1> Golden Blue Diamond Pendant<br>
Rough Silver Chain (quested no drop item)<br>
Any of those WW dragon talismans<br>
Shrouded Medallion (drops in Maiden's)<br>
Kunzar Cloak for fire<br>
Diamond Electrum Mask as well<br>
<br>
The list goes on but really if you have diamonds/blue diamonds then you've got starter suggestions. By the way -- hehe -- levels matter more than resist gear. Since gaining 5 levels I don't even wear half the stuff anymore. <p><br>
