<br>
Because on a raid you're as good as dead if you don't have hight resists, but you might as well be dead if you trade out all your wis gear for SV.<br>
<br>
Hmm, easy to get: crystalline eye of Shardwurm in GD. 10 sv m/c/f and some mana. Also if you get low on wis in resist gear try for that wedding ring from ToFS. For range, go frozen orb for CR and grail of (justice (?)) from scarlet for FR (both have same wis but orb has more mana).<br>
<br>
And, of course, if you have the time and means get your epic and 7th coldain shawl.<br>
<br>
But as someone said above, level is key. A 55 with 255 all resists will still get hit more than a 60 with 150+.   <p><left><font face=arial color=black size=2><b> <BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=69903">Milwein Fenrir</A>
